The readings marked 'required' must be read carefully prior to class. Students
are encouraged to prepare short outlines based on reading notes before coming
to class. The readings marked 'recommended' are suggested to supplement, deepen
and expand the issues raised by the required readings. While students don't
have to read them all before class, they are strongly encouraged to read what
they can in order to fully realize the potential of this course.
